query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from tag AS t1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('abstract-algebra',
'definite-integrals',
'differential-geometry',
'discrete-mathematics',
'elementary-number-theory',
'exponential-function',
'linear-algebra',
'notation',
'partitioning',
'permissions',
'probability-distributions',
'random-variables') AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 0
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.question_id = q1.id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id group by t1.name;
